Why Java String immutable hoti hai?

Answer (Real Time)

Security + Performance + Thread safety ke liye.

üß† Real-Time Example
String token = "abc123";


Agar String mutable hoti:

Koi bhi thread token change kar deta

Security breach ho jata (login/session token)

