Difference between == and .equals()
‚ùì Question

== aur .equals() me difference?

üß† Real-Time Example (Login validation)
String dbPassword = new String("admin");
String userPassword = new String("admin");

System.out.println(dbPassword == userPassword);      // false
System.out.println(dbPassword.equals(userPassword)); // true

Explanation

== ‚Üí memory reference compare

equals() ‚Üí content compare

‚û°Ô∏è Login check hamesha equals() se
