3Ô∏è‚É£ Why StringBuilder preferred over String?
‚ùì Question

Loop me StringBuilder kyun use karte ho?

üß† Real-Time Example (Log generation)
for(int i=0;i<1000;i++){
   result.append(i);
}

‚úÖ Reason

String ‚Üí har time new object
StringBuilder ‚Üí same object modify

‚û°Ô∏è Performance fast hoti hai

4.Exception vs Error
‚ùì Question

Exception aur Error ka difference?

üß† Real-Time Example

Exception ‚Üí NullPointerException (recoverable)

Error ‚Üí OutOfMemoryError (non-recoverable)

‚û°Ô∏è Exception handle kar sakte hain
‚û°Ô∏è Error nahi
-----------------------------------
6Ô∏è‚É£ Checked vs Unchecked Exception
üß† Real-Time Example
FileInputStream fis = new FileInputStream("data.txt"); // Checked
int a = 10 / 0; // Unchecked

Checked	Unchecked
Compile time	Runtime
IOException	ArithmeticException
